text: Hello, Frisco, Hello is a 1943 American musical comedy movie directed by H. Bruce Humberstone. It stars Alice Faye, John Payne, Jack Oakie, Lynn Bari, Laird Cregar, June Havoc, Ward Bond, Aubrey Mather, John Archer, Frank Orth and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. It won 1 Oscar and was nominated for an Academy Award in 1944. == Other websites == * * * * Category:1943 comedy movies Category:1943 musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by H. Bruce Humberstone
